channel.title: Change Levels?
channel.description:
If this question has been answered before, sorry. I tried searching google but couldn't really find the answer.
I did a windows recovery (be on the safe side of a possible virus and what not) and I lost everything because I don't have the resources for a back up just yet. I tried using a DVDR-cd as a USB device and it seemed like things were working until I went to put it back into the computer and nothing was on it. Tsk. So my question is whether or not there is a way to get to a later chapter using the console or if there are saved level uploads somewhere I can download? I was on Residue Processing.
